OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRoyal Mail staff to stage  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffour-day strike action     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some 115,000 Royal Mail workers are set
OL,6, to strike on four days in August and   
OL,7, September in a dispute over pay.       
OL,9,FThe Communication Workers Union (CWU)  
OL,10,Fsaid workers would walk out on 26 and  
OL,11,F31 August and 8 and 9 September.       
OL,13,FThe move comes as Royal Mail said the  
OL,14,Funion had rejected a pay rise offer    
OL,15,F"worth up to 5.5%" after three months  
OL,16,Fof talks.                              
OL,18,FUnion bosses the action was "for a     
OL,19,Fproper pay rise" and said the strikes  
OL,20,Fwould be the biggest this summer.      
